{"type":null,"faqId":15308,"title":"Hol-U19: Edit/delete/view/send Mail？","answer":"<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Calibri','sans-serif'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><span>Main menu-&gt;Email-&gt;input user ID and password.</span></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Calibri','sans-serif'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><span>Account setting:</span></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Calibri','sans-serif'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><span>1. Manual</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: 宋体\">：</span></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: left; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Calibri','sans-serif'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\" align=\"left\"><span>Input ID and password-&gt;POP3</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings\"><span>à</span></span><span>Inter the server setting interface</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings\"><span>à</span></span><span>edit the POP3 server</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings\"><span>à</span></span><span>Next</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings\"><span>à</span></span><span>setting the send SMTP server</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings\"><span>à</span></span><span>next</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings\"><span>à</span></span><span>setting the frequency of sync mail</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: Wingdings\"><span>à</span></span><span>next-&gt;setting the mail as prompt.</span></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Calibri','sans-serif'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><span>2. Auto</span></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; FONT-FAMILY: 'Calibri','sans-serif'; FONT-SIZE: 12pt\"><span>Input ID and password-&gt;Next-&gt;Mail setting-&gt;finish.</span></p>\n<p style=\"TEXT-JUSTIFY: inter-ideograph; TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN: 0c